{"id":671,"date":"2024-05-03T01:45:43","date_gmt":"2024-05-03T01:45:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8888\/?post_type=product&#038;p=671"},"modified":"2025-07-28T04:48:00","modified_gmt":"2025-07-28T04:48:00","slug":"niacinamide-15","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8888\/product\/niacinamide-15\/","title":{"rendered":"NIACINAMIDE 15%"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2>L\u1ee2I \u00cdCH:<\/h2>\n<h3>C\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u1ea9m<\/h3>\n<p>Niacinamide th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a enzym ceramide synthase &#8211; \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 enzym ch\u00ednh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p ceramide. Khi enzyme n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t ceramide s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean, c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/p>\n<h3>Gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u1ee5n<\/h3>\n<p>Niacinamide l\u00e0 1 trong 2 lo\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<br \/>\nNiacinamide \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a s\u1ef1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u ti\u1ebft ra v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00edt t\u1eafc, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<h3>Gi\u1ea3m s\u1eafc t\u1ed1, th\u00e2m n\u00e1m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da<\/h3>\n<p>Niacinamide \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n melanin \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u00e2m, n\u00e1m, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<h3>Gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da<\/h3>\n<p>Niacinamide c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho da m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/p>\n<h3>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, Niacinamide gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2276\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8888\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/7-Serum-thu-nho-lo-chan-long-Niacinamide-15_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2122\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8888\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/7-Serum-thu-nho-lo-chan-long-Niacinamide-15_.jpg 1500w, http:\/\/localhost:8888\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/7-Serum-thu-nho-lo-chan-long-Niacinamide-15_-212x300.jpg 212w, http:\/\/localhost:8888\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/7-Serum-thu-nho-lo-chan-long-Niacinamide-15_-724x1024.jpg 724w, http:\/\/localhost:8888\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/7-Serum-thu-nho-lo-chan-long-Niacinamide-15_-768x1086.jpg 768w, http:\/\/localhost:8888\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/7-Serum-thu-nho-lo-chan-long-Niacinamide-15_-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, http:\/\/localhost:8888\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/7-Serum-thu-nho-lo-chan-long-Niacinamide-15_-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, http:\/\/loca